---
config:
  theme: base
  sequence:
    showSequenceNumbers: true
    mirrorActors: false
    actorMargin: 70
  themeVariables:
    fontFamily: "'Open Sans', arial, sans-serif"
    actorBkg: '#cdf3ff'
    actorBorder: '#007298'
    actorTextColor: '#333E48'
    activationBkgColor: '#fff4cc'
    activationBorderColor: '#e77204'
    sequenceNumberColor: '#45842a'
    noteBkgColor: '#dbffcc'
    noteBorderColor: '#45842a'
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor Client
  participant API as API Gateway
  participant Worker
  participant DB as Database

  Client->>API: Submit order
  activate API
  API->>DB: Reserve inventory
  DB-->>API: Reservation id
  create participant Job as Fulfillment Job
  API->>Job: Schedule pick list
  API-->>Client: Accepted
  deactivate API
  Worker->>Job: Process queue item
  Job-->>Worker: Complete
  Note over Client,Worker: EFX blue actors, yellow activations, green notes

